                                <incipit>Gloria in excelsis deo</incipit>
                                <explicit defective="true">nostre carnis uisibiliter corporalis apparuit</explicit>
                                <note>Seven or eight leaves are missing after <locus from="107v" to="107v" scheme="folios"/> resulting in the loss of the majority of the Ordo, including the Canon. <!--ingen förlust mellan 105v 106r-->
                                </note>
                            </msItem>
