                                <explicit>pro cuius solemnitate precepimus tua sancta letantes Per</explicit>
                                <note>
                                    <p> The proper of saints begins with the vigil of St Andrew (29 Nov.) and ends with the feast of St Katharine (25 Nov.).</p>
                                    <p> Notable feasts:</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="153v" to="153v" scheme="folios"/>: St Cunigunde (3 Mar.);</p>
